    "summary": "Repair the existing #96851 contributor branch against current main so accepted sessions_spawn launches are not persisted as tool failures at the source. Current main already includes the merged #96842 compaction-summary suppression, so the repair should keep only the remaining embedded-runner classification fix and drop/resolve duplicate compaction changes during rebase.",
    "pr_title": "fix(agents): stop recording accepted sessions_spawn launches as tool failures",
    "pr_body": "## What Problem This Solves\nAccepted `sessions_spawn` launches can still be persisted as `isError: true` by the embedded runner path, even though current main already suppresses legacy accepted-spawn entries in compaction summaries via #96842. That leaves the source-side transcript classification half of #96833 unresolved.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\nThis repairs #96851 on the contributor branch now that #96842 has merged. The branch should be rebased onto bc7f0f1223cd760ab812eeab526e02ae6ae27d68, drop duplicate compaction changes already present on main, and keep the narrow embedded-runner accepted `sessions_spawn` classification fix.\n\n## User Impact\nAccepted child-run launches should no longer be recorded as tool failures in new transcripts, and existing compaction safeguards continue to ignore legacy accepted-spawn error entries.\n\n## Evidence\n- Current main still computes `isError` from `event.isError === true` in `src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/extensions.ts:92` and returns `isError: true` at `src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/extensions.ts:104`.\n- Current main already skips accepted `sessions_spawn` legacy failures in `src/agents/agent-hooks/compaction-safeguard.ts:456` through `src/agents/agent-hooks/compaction-safeguard.ts:465` from #96842.\n- Run `pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner.extensions.test.ts src/agents/agent-hooks/compaction-safeguard.test.ts` and `pnpm check:changed` after repair.",
    "likely_files": [
      "src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/extensions.ts",
      "src/agents/embedded-agent-runner.extensions.test.ts"
    ],
    "validation_commands": [
      "pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner.extensions.test.ts src/agents/agent-hooks/compaction-safeguard.test.ts",
      "pnpm check:changed"
    ],
    "credit_notes": [
      "Repair contributor branch for @parveshsaini's #96851 rather than replacing it; preserve author credit in the PR history and final PR body.",
      "Mention that #96842 by @nxmxbbd already landed the compaction-summary half on main and that this repair keeps the remaining source-side classification behavior.",
      "Issue credit: #96833 was opened by @Neomail2 and supplied the root reproduction."
    ],
